PLEX can be used to add 30 days of Clone State Omega time to your account or to unlock special character and account services.

<font color="#ff3399cc">Tip: Purchasing PLEX to sell for ISK to other players can be a good way to kickstart your capsuleer career.</font>

<font size="14">Buying PLEX</font>
You can buy PLEX on the regional market for ISK or securely on <url=https://secure.eveonline.com/PLEX/>https://secure.eveonline.com/PLEX/</url> using conventional payment methods.

<font size="14">Using PLEX</font>
The primary usage for PLEX is to add 30 days of Clone State Omega time to your account. It can also be used for the following:

Convert to AUR: A PLEX can be exchanged for 3500 AUR, the currency used in the New Eden Store where unique fashion accessories, cosmetic ship upgrades and various other services are sold.

Multiple character training: Activate 30 days of passive skill gain on additional characters on your account with PLEX. This can also be done using a <url=showinfo:34133>Multiple Pilot Training Certificate</url> which is sold in the New Eden Store.
